version_description: Live version has added bass notes to chords for fuller sound, 5th fret capo and transcribed by eye from video.

This version is for camp fire playing.

This song has the lyrics to Metallica's One, however it is played and sung to the tune of U2's Version of one. Versus with AM/D7/Gmaj7/G lift and hammer index finger on ever chord played. On Versus with C/Cmaj9/B/AM/G only play the base note on the Cmaj9/b and G, between C chords lift middle, 3 quick Up down up down, then hammer the middle finger to start 2nd C Chord.
